<subSubSection id="639F46D25C6A09218ADD33A87A79BAA9" pageId="2" pageNumber="29" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="1365D87ED3421603CB39A0B95EE6EB8D" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F356EFAA17103A11526AE2161E2C79AF" pageId="2" pageNumber="29">The genus is currently known only from the Arava Valley, Israel.</paragraph>
